add experimental support for a syntax like:
blockname (inherit="foo") {
  ...
}

Change the way Project#previous_builds is calculated

Probably a performance gain, but it doesn't matter -- it should save us
from count/size weirdness =)

blog : refactor the init/installation to make adding a blog module a one line addition to an app's _init.js

Add a blog by :

  routes.<path> = core.blog.install({});

blog : modified to make it easier to insert into an existing app

To insert :

iroutes = new Routes();
routes.geir = Blog.routes;
